  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The year is 275 B.C. Through conquest and careful diplomacy, the Roman republic has brought the petty kingdoms and city-states of Italia under its control. This is the moment at which the heirs of Romulus and Remus step onto the world stage. This is the humble beginning of an empire that will one day cover most of Europe, Asia Minor, and North Africa.\n\nAs an ambitious young officer, you duty is to defend Rome. Your hope is to become Caesar. Your fate - to rule the world.",
